                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-19-18761120 t18761120-19-punishment-15"></join>Six Month's Imprisonment</rs>
                  </hi>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">LORD</hi>—<hi rend="smallCaps">
